NEW ERA ELECTRON said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 16.47% to NT$92,434,000 from NT$110,657,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             92,434          110,657    
YOY%             -16.47%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            371,602          404,466    
YOY%              -8.13% 
=================================================================
 